  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development Executive (Recruitment)",
  "description": "<p><strong>⭐ Why Join MCI Career Services?</strong></p><p>At MCI Career Services, we don’t just sell a service — we connect talents with opportunities and help our clients build strong teams. If you enjoy meeting people, closing deals, and are motivated by performance-based earnings, this role offers strong career growth and uncapped potential.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Get (Benefits)</strong></p><ul><li><p>Monthly sales commission</p></li><li><p>Bi-annual increment opportunities</p></li><li><p>Incentive trips</p></li><li><p>Continuous learning, coaching, and career development</p></li><li><p>Strong internal support from Business Development & Talent Acquisition teams</p></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li><p>Identify and develop new business opportunities through market research and outreach</p></li><li><p>Generate leads via cold calling, networking, and client engagement</p></li><li><p>Conduct client presentations, manage negotiations, and close recruitment deals</p></li><li><p>Build and manage a healthy sales pipeline from prospecting to conversion</p></li><li><p>Understand client hiring needs and propose suitable recruitment solutions</p></li><li><p>Maintain long-term client relationships and provide strong after-sales support</p></li><li><p>Track sales activities and maintain accurate records in CRM systems</p></li><li><p>Collaborate closely with Talent Acquisition consultants to meet client expectations</p></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in any discipline (business-related fields preferred)</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and organisational skills</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, willingness to learn, and confidence in engaging clients</p></li><li><p>Results-driven and motivated to achieve sales targets</p></li><li></li></ul><p>Applicants who possess relevant experience for the above responsibilities are most welcome to apply. If you do not possess the above experience, your application will still be considered on individual merits and you may be contacted for other opportunities.</p><p>Please submit your updated resume in MS Words format by using the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by the company relating to this job application.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf</a></p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p><strong>Jong Si Xiang</strong><br /><strong>Registration Number: R25157567</strong><br /><strong>EA Licence No: 06C2859 (MCI Career Services Pte Ltd)</strong></p>",
